Place the cream in a chilled metal bowl or mixer bowl. With a whisk, or the whisk attachment, whip the cream until slightly frothy. Sprinkle in the sugar and continue to whip until soft peaks form. Use immediately, or refrigerate for up to 1 hour. TO MAKE COCOA WHIPPED CREAM: Combine the sugar with 1 tablespoon plus 1 teaspoon unsweetened cocoa powder before adding it to the cream.